.commands: .help - Get help. [n] .get ip - Get IP Address. [n] .cmd reload - Reload the page. [n] .cmd open app - Redirect to app. [n] .get data - Get a list of data points. [n] .cmd clear data - Clear all current data. [n] .cmd clear client - Clear all client data. [n] .cmd helper enable - Start Autohelp on init. [n] .cmd helper disable - Cancel Autohelp on init. [n] .cmd timestamp enable - Show time stamps at init. [n] .cmd timestamp disable - Hide time stamps at init.
